{"id":881,"date":"2026-01-24T19:45:15","date_gmt":"2026-01-24T19:45:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/?p=881"},"modified":"2026-03-14T04:56:07","modified_gmt":"2026-03-14T04:56:07","slug":"home-in-a-hot-pot","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/home-in-a-hot-pot\/","title":{"rendered":"Home in a Hot Pot"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<section class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-post-banner section-post-banner\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><div class=\"t-box t-box-a\"><h1 class=\"hg\">HOME IN A HOT POT<\/h1><div class=\"i-line\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-b\"><div class=\"container-studies\"><div class=\"label-studies\">FORM STUDY<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">thesis<\/div><\/div><div class=\"container-roles\"><div class=\"label-roles\">ROLE<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">concept<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">design<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">motion<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-c\"><div class=\"media-wrapper\"><div class=\"media-overlay\"><div class=\"media-overlay-placeholder--mask\"><div class=\"media-overlay-placeholder--text\">Visit Full Video<\/div><\/div><\/div><a class=\"t-media-wrapper\" href=\"https:\/\/vimeo.com\/1094209424\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><video class=\"t-media\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/jgunarto_hotpot_final.mp4\" loop muted playsinline autoplay><\/video><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"section-post-detail\" class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-post-detail\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><header class=\"t-box-a post-detail__meta\"><div class=\"post-detail__heading\">(PROJECT DETAIL)<\/div><div class=\"post-info\"><div class=\"post-info__item\"><div class=\"post-info__item-background\"><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-label\">MEDIUM<\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-value\">collage, 2d, 3d, mixed media<\/div><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item\"><div class=\"post-info__item-background\"><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-label\">TOOLS<\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-value\">ADOBE AFTER EFFECTS, ILLUSTRATOR, PHOTOSHOP, dragonframe, CINEMA 4D<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/header><div class=\"t-box-b post-detail__body\"><nav class=\"post-detail__tabs\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-dot is--active\"><\/div><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab is--active\">OVERVIEW<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">CHALLENGE<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">REFLECTION<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">SCRIPT<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">AWARDS<\/div><\/ul><\/nav><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body\"><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-body-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item is--active\">A mixed-media animation exploring family dynamics through the metaphor of a shared hot pot meal.<br>Told through visual metaphors and narration, the story unfolds using hand-crafted food elements and expressive typography.<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">How do you capture family dynamics (love, some tension, and tradition) without the usual anthropomorphic characters? &#8211; this was the question.<br>Early design and animation were all done digitally, which felt cold and lacked some certain feeling.<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">Finalizing the design style while encapsulating all mediums into one that would appeal to the general audience, touching people&#8217;s hearts through the message of family is what made this project successful. Wouldn&#8217;t work without the constant feedback applied and hot pot helpers!<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">Every family&#8217;s a unique blend of ingredients. Simmering with potential. Loving, nurturing, and complex, with just a dash of spice. Through playful clashes, we come together. Experience balances flavor and adds depth. Love can be tender, or can be firm. Sure, there is the occasional tangle. But with love and a little bit of patience, things seem to work out. Family is the broth that holds all our flavors together. Ciak! Let&#8217;s eat!<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">2025:<br>\u2022 Collision Award Gold Winner (General-Student)<br>\u2022 Tokyo Film &amp; Screenplay Awards (Selected, Animation)<br>\u2022 Best Hollywood Day Short Film Festival (Selected, Animation)<br>\u2022 New York Lift-Off Film Festival (Selected, Animation)<br><br>2026:<br>\u2022 LA Film &amp; Documentary Awards Winner (Best Animation)<\/div><\/ul><\/div><div class=\"post-detail__media-container\"><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/early_02-1.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/early_02-1.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/early_03-1-scaled-1.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/early_03-1-scaled-1.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/hotpot_styleframe5.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/hotpot_styleframe5.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/early_01-1.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/early_01-1.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/jgunarto_gold_collision.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/jgunarto_gold_collision.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-post-gallery section-post-gallery\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><div class=\"t-box t-box-a\"><h2 class=\"hg\">DESIGN <\/h2><div class=\"i-line\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-b\"><div class=\"caption-1\">(INFO)<\/div><div class=\"t-body\">Hand-painted of the human touch, mixed with digital ELEMENTS. The blend brought warmth, contrast, and a sense of home.<\/div><div class=\"caption-2\">SCROLL DOWN<\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-c\"><div class=\"container-media\"><div class=\"t-cr item-media\"><div class=\"t-box media-number\"><div class=\"media-number__current\">01<\/div><div class=\"media-number__i-circle\"><svg width=\"4\" height=\"4\" viewBox=\"0 0 4 4\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><ellipse cx=\"1.87005\" cy=\"1.83572\" rx=\"1.82122\" ry=\"1.83108\" fill=\"#EBEAE4\"><\/ellipse><\/svg><\/div><div class=\"media-number__total\">05<\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box wrapper-media-image\"><picture class=\"media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/hotpot_styleframe2-1-1.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/hotpot_styleframe2-1-1.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-cr item-media\"><div class=\"t-box media-number\"><div class=\"media-number__current\">02<\/div><div class=\"media-number__i-circle\"><svg width=\"4\" height=\"4\" viewBox=\"0 0 4 4\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><ellipse cx=\"1.87005\" cy=\"1.83572\" rx=\"1.82122\" ry=\"1.83108\" fill=\"#EBEAE4\"><\/ellipse><\/svg><\/div><div class=\"media-number__total\">05<\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box wrapper-media-image\"><picture class=\"media-image\"><source media=\"(max-